(361, 1, '2022-05-25 06:31:57', '2022-05-25 06:31:57', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rainer Herzog is a well-versed executive in the healthcare industry, drawing on a long history of international experience.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He has successfully built-up new business areas in his career, opening up new market potentials and achieving long-term commercial success.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rainer possesses management know-how in different sectors of healthcare, such as life sciences, medical technology or digital health. He has an extensive international network of decision-makers, opinion leaders and senior executives from politics, industry, research and academia.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rainer began his career at Roche Diagnostics in France and subsequently headed international marketing for cardiology at Schwarz Pharma AG in Monheim, Germany.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After joining Swedish telecom equipment supplier Ericsson, Rainer was responsible for setting up and managing the company\'s \"Digital Health\" business unit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For the global digital health stakeholder organization HIMSS (Health Information Management Systems Society), Rainer first served as Managing Director Europe, and later as General Manager for Germany, Austria and Switzerland.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He also managed 2 successful European telemedicine projects - MobiHealth and HealthService24.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Rainer studied European Business Management in London and Reutlingen and lives in Munich.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Rainer Herzog', 'Rainer Herzog is a well-versed executive in the healthcare industry, drawing on a long history of international experience.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rainer-herzog', '', '', '2022-05-2