(243, 1, '2022-04-29 21:44:34', '2022-04-29 21:44:34', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This survey, conducted between January and March 2018 in 13 European countries, sought to evaluate the awareness and access to mexiletine and subsequent harm caused by limited treatment access.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":234,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://admedicum.test/app/uploads/2022/04/case-studies-5-img.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-234\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Qualitative semi-structured interviews with patient organisations or independent patient representatives and myotonia specialists. The interviews, using a bespoke questionnaire (10) , were focused on obtaining data on the overall treatment of NDM, and the outcomes for patients not having access to treatment.</li><li>Quantitative online-survey (11) that was aimed at verifying the data collected in the interviews and further establishing the diagnosis, symptoms, treatments and access to treatments for patients with NDM.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The online patient survey included 37 participants with confirmed MC in 6 European countries. Of the patients taking mexiletine, 84% had been prescribed mexiletine by a neurologist. Other patients were prescribed mexiletine by cardiologists, general practitioners, ophthalmologists, pneumologist and rheumatologists. Difficulty in obtaining mexiletine was experienced (multiple answers applied to some patients)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Patient Reports', 'There are a lot of impressive stories about how \"the rare ones\" deal with their daily challenges', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'enhancing-clinical-trial-recruitment', '', '', '2022-05-25 03:32:34', '2022-05-25 03:32:34', '', 0, 'http://admedicum.test/?post_type=case-studies&#038;p=243', 0, 'case-studies', '', 0),
(244, 1, '2022-04-29 21:53:43', '2022-04-29 21:53:43', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The client needed assistance recruiting patients for a phase I/II trial in a disease area with many other simultaneously ongoing clinical trials. In addition to the typical local site recruitment strategies, the client wants to investigate other ways of sharing clinical trial information with the potential patient community and the public.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":240,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://admedicum.test/app/uploads/2022/04/NoPath-copia-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-240\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Co-creating a Patient Landing Page with patients that includes online pre-screening and patient concierge service</li><li>Simultaneously launching a landing page for relevant physicians</li><li>Designing information materials with patient input for referring physicians to share with their patients</li><li>Approval of all materials by Ethics Committee prior to public launch</li><li>Joint dissemination of trial information through patient groups, social media and potential referring physicians</li><li>Supporting further contact with highly targeted online and social media advertising</li><li>Production of educational videos and a video on the personal decision-making process of a patient considering participation in the clinical trial</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>A significantly higher number of patients screened faster through direct involvement</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Watch our <a href=\"https://www.admedicum.com/en/news-details/webinar-series-2-enhancing-clinical-trial-recruitment-successful-industry-strategies-using-patient-engagement\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://www.admedicum.com/en/news-details/webinar-series-2-enhancing-clinical-trial-recruitment-successful-industry-strategies-using-patient-engagement\">webinar </a>on the topic of enhancing clinical trial recruitment using patient engagement</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Enhancing Clinical Trial Recruitment', 'The client needed assistance recruiting patients for a phase I/II trial in a disease area with many other simultaneously ongoing clinical trials', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'co-creating-clinical-trial-design-and-recruitment-strategy', '', '', '2022-05-24 20:26:25', '2022-05-24 20:26:25', '', 0, 'http://admedicum.test/?post_type=case-studies&#038;p=244', 0, 'case-studies', '', 0),
(245, 1, '2022-04-29 21:46:48', '2022-04-29 21:46:48', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A company is developing a new medical product for patients with a rare disease. Additional services, e.g., a patient-support-program (PSP), are considered important to help patients gaining access to new treatments when needed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is a lack of knowledge about what program elements will be helpful for patients and relatives, what would be just “nice-to-have” and what can potentially be perceived as inappropriate.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":235,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://admedicum.test/app/uploads/2022/04/case-studies-6-img.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-235\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Problem Analysis, Patient Segmentation, and Program Targeting</li><li>Identification of best partners among patient experts</li><li>Co-creation session prepared and moderated by admedicum</li><li>Challenging status quo and identifying need-gaps</li><li>Brainstorming opportunities for further improvements of program components</li><li>Validation among “normal patients”</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Strong basis for a PSP that truly benefits patients and achieves the client’s goals</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Co-creating a Patient Support Program', 'A company is developing a new medical product for patients with a rare disease', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'developing-a-patient-advisory-board', '', '', '2022-05-25 04:33:01', '2022-05-25 04:33:01', '', 0, 'http://admedicum.test/?post_type=case-studies&#038;p=245', 0, 'case-studies', '', 0),
(246, 1, '2022-04-29 21:52:20', '2022-04-29 21:52:20', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A client would like to establish a European patient advisory board to guide upcoming clinical trials, act as a sounding board to hear patient concerns first-hand and get regular advice from patient advocates on a variety of topics in R&amp;D.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For compliance and data protection reasons, the client does not want to be in direct contact with individual patients or collect their data. The company does not know the right patient experts, how to identify them, and are unsure how to ensure an efficient and compliant dialogue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":232,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://admedicum.test/app/uploads/2022/04/case-studies-3-img.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-232\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Developing a charter describing the mission of the Patient Advisory Board Identification of best patient advisors for the clients’ Patient Advisory Board<br>Facilitation by admedicum of the first Advisory Board covering topics including:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Clinical Trial Design</li><li>PROs/QoL</li><li>Patient-friendly informed consent form</li><li>Recruitment strategy</li><li>atient Support Program</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Continuous exchange with a standing, high-quality Patient Advisory Board</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Developing a Patient Advisory Board', 'The client would like to establish a European patient advisory board to guide upcoming', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'supporting-patient-access-to-treatment', '', '', '2022-05-25 04:31:05', '2022-05-25 04:31:05', '', 0, 'http://admedicum.test/?post_type=case-studies&#038;p=246', 0, 'case-studies', '', 0),
(247, 1, '2022-04-29 21:53:19', '2022-04-29 21:53:19', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The client needs to obtain the patient view and preferences on clinical trial design, especially regarding the burden of the trial, in- and exclusion criteria and the readability of consent material. The client had not previously involved patients in clinical trial design and has no structure and procedures in place for gathering patient feedback.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":231,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://admedicum.test/app/uploads/2022/04/case-studies-2-img.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-231\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Patient representatives with HTA experience review the target product profile of the clients’ asset</li><li>Full review of the development plan and trial design regarding patient relevance</li><li>Gap analysis emphasizing patient-relevant aspects</li><li>Discuss and challenge recruitment &amp; retention strategy</li><li>Joint session with the client’s internal team to discuss findings</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Highly patient-relevant trial design regarding HTA and clinical outcomes and capturing patient needs and preferences for efficient recruiting and retention</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Co-Creating Clinical Trial Design and Recruitment Strategy', 'The client needs to obtain the patient view and preferences on clinical trial design', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'co-creating-a-patient-support-program-2', '', '', '2022-05-25 04:28:25', '2022-05-25 04:28:25', '', 0, 'http://admedicum.test/?post_type=case-studies&#038;p=247', 0, 'case-studies', '', 0),
(249, 1, '2022-04-29 21:48:40', '2022-04-29 21:48:40', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Patients with non-dystrophic myotonic disorders (NDM) experience unpredictable frequency and severity of myotonic episodes, associated with life-long symptoms and negative impact on physical functioning and quality of life. Treatment has included unlicensed products such as mexiletine.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For the European Medicines Agency to maintain the Orphan Drug Designation, data was necessary to evaluate the use and access to mexiletine across Europe. There is limited data on the impact of and disrupted availability of mexiletine in the EU.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":279,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://admedicum.test/app/uploads/2022/05/case-studies-4-img.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-279\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Leading the creation of the Myotonia Observation Survey of Patient Access to Therapy avoiding Harm (MyoPath)</li><li>Using a well-defined mixed methodology of interviews and an online survey to gather information on the availability and use of mexiletine in the EU by patients with NDM in a short time frame</li><li>Gathering important data regarding patient use of mexiletine and the harm due to lack of treatment access</li><li>Presenting results of the survey to the Committee for Orphan Medicinal Products (COMP) along with the client. Read the COMP\'s public assessment report</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The COMP maintained the orphan drug status of mexiletine which will significantly support patient access across Europe. admedicum thereby helped the internal team to create great value both for patients and their company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Supporting Patient Access to Treatment', 'In order for the European Medicines Agency to maintain the marketing authorization', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'co-creating-a-patient-support-program', '', '', '2022-05-25 04:32:10', '2022-05-25 04:32:10', '', 0, 'http://admedicum.test/?post_type=case-studies&#038;p=249', 0, 'case-studies', '', 0),
