(335, 1, '2022-05-25 04:20:57', '2022-05-25 04:20:57', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Multimedia Production of Patient-Relevant Content</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The client wants to create content in collaboration with patients and tell their personal stories but can\'t get in direct contact. Another common situation is the client wants to create content for patients that are tailored to the needs and interests of this target group and needs a reliable partner for this who understands the patient\'s point of view and can create meaningful, diverse, and creative content.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3><strong>Our Solution</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We create this content in co-creation or consultation with patients. We prepare the relevant information in an appealing and professional way that corresponds to the respective format and intended use.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"100%\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":279,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://admedicum.test/app/uploads/2022/05/case-studies-4-img.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-279\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Podcasts<br>Texts<br>Images<br>Videos <br>Graphics </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We deliver content ranging from a single media to complete websites.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In any case, all these formats will be adapted in their style to the respective purpose.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Multimedia Content Creation', 'The client wants to create content in collaboration with patients and tell their personal stories but can\'t get in direct contact.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '311-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-25 04:20:57', '2022-05-25 04:20:57', '', 311, 'http://admedicum.test/?p=335', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(336, 1, '2022-05-25 04:23:26', '2022-05-25 04:23:26', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A client wishes to submit an HTA dossier to a payer institution for a therapeutic indication with many other approved treatments already existing on the market. The client did not previously consult patients or patient organizations in the development of the Patient Reported Outcomes data and is unsure how to approach it. The patient relevance of the data has been questioned and is not well justified by the company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Identification of best partners among KOLs, allied health professionals and patient experts</li><li>Co-creation session prepared and moderated by admedicum</li><li>Full-day session jointly with the internal team </li><li>Challenging status quo and identifying the need-gap</li><li>Brainstorming opportunities for further clinical and health economic evidence</li><li>Conceptualizing a plan for additional QoL/PROMs data</li><li>points acceptable to the company</li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img alt=\"\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>HTA relevant Real-World Evidence (RWE) ideas as a basis for internal decision making in future data collection</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Multi-Stakeholder Co-Creation on Real-World Evidence', 'A client wishes to submit an HTA dossier to a payer institution for a therapeutic indication with many other approved treatments', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '306-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-25 04:23:26', '2022-05-25 04:23:26', '', 306, 'http://admedicum.test/?p=336', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(337, 1, '2022-05-25 04:27:08', '2022-05-25 04:27:08', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The client is beginning to design a clinical trial protocol for a new phase I/II trial in a poorly understood, under diagnosed, and rare genetic disorder with no other current treatments. There are only about 50 families affected by the condition in Europe without any formal patient association. To meet enrolment targets, the client will have to make a compelling case on the value of their treatment to families and to establish trust.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The client needs to understand the burden of the disease, challenges, everyday life, preferences and hopes for the future of families affected by this genetic disease. The client’s compliance department felt it was best for the interviews to be done by an outside entity.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":233,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://admedicum.test/app/uploads/2022/04/case-studies-4-img.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-233\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Designing a qualitative interview guide, co-created with patients, and aligned with the client’s needs</li><li>Setting up a quantitative screening survey for an appropriate recruitment process</li><li>Conducting exploratory semi-structured interviews with patients and with other stakeholders like KOLs, HCPs, caregivers, etc. when deemed necessary</li><li>Visualization of the patient pathway</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Obtaining important insights into the patient pathway and detection of relevant health care gaps</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Patient Dialogue about Patient Pathway to Assist Clinical Trial Recruitment', 'The client is beginning to design a clinical trial protocol for a new phase I/II trial in a poorly understood, under diagnosed, and rare genetic', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '303-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-25 04:27:08', '2022-05-25 04:27:08', '', 303, 'http://admedicum.test/?p=337', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(338, 1, '2022-05-25 04:28:15', '2022-05-25 04:28:15', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Situation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The client needs to obtain the patient view and preferences on clinical trial design, especially regarding the burden of the trial, in- and exclusion criteria and the readability of consent material. The client had not previously involved patients in clinical trial design and has no structure and procedures in place for gathering patient feedback.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Our Solution</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Patient representatives with HTA experience review the target product profile of the clients’ asset</li><li>Full review of the development plan and trial design regarding patient relevance</li><li>Gap analysis emphasizing patient-relevant aspects</li><li>Discuss and challenge recruitment &amp; retention strategy</li><li>Joint session with the client’s internal team to discuss findings</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Results</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Highly patient-relevant trial design regarding HTA and clinical outcomes and capturing patient needs and preferences for efficient recruiting and retention</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Co-Creating Clinical Trial Design and Recruitment Strategy', 'The client needs to obtain the patient view and preferences on clinical trial design', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '247-autosave-v1', '', '', '2022-05-25 04:28:15', '2022-05-25 04:28:15', '', 247, 'http://admedicum.test/?p=338', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
