(353, 1, '2022-05-25 06:19:10', '2022-05-25 06:19:10', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dr. Meike Neukirchen is a licensed phamacist with more than 12 years experience in pharmaceutical industry.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Experience</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>More than 12 years experience in clinical research / drug development</li><li>Know-how in planning, conducting, analysis and reporting of clinical trials</li><li>Practical knowledge in industrial production of drugs</li><li>Pharmacist in different retail pharmacies</li><li>Experienced in communication with patients, relatives, medical doctors and caregivers</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dr. Meike Neukirchen studied pharmacy in Marburg and in Paris. Afterwards she earned her Ph.D. at the LMU Munich in the field of immunology (Prof. Dr. Gunther Hartmann).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Publications (extract)</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dahan A, Boom M, Sarton E, Hay J, Groeneveld GJ, Neukirchen M, Bothmer J, Aarts L, Olofsen E.<br>Respiratory Effects of the Nociceptin/Orphanin FQ Peptide and Opioid Receptor Agonist, Cebranopadol, in Healthy Human Volunteers.<br>Anesthesiology. 2017 Apr;126(4):697-707.<br>&nbsp;<br>Boom M, Olofsen E, Neukirchen M, Fussen R, Hay J, Groeneveld GJ, Aarts L, Sarton E, Dahan A.<br>Fentanyl utility function: a risk-benefit composite of pain relief and breathing responses.<br>Anesthesiology. 2013 Sep;119(3):663-74<br>&nbsp;<br>Bekeredjian-Ding I*, Schäfer M*, Hartmann E, Pries R, Parcina M, Schneider P, Giese T, Endres S, Wollenberg B, Hartmann G*: contributed equally<br>Tumor-derived Prostaglandin E2 and TGF-beta synergize to inhibit PDC-derived IFN-alpha.<br>Immunology 2009; 128: 439-450</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Contact:.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>meike.neukirchen@admedicum.com</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>+49 2236 94733 66 (60)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/meike-neukirchen/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">LinkedIn</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Dr. Meike Neukirchen', 'Dr. Meike Neukirchen is a licensed phamacist with more than 12 years experience in pharmaceutical industry.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dr-meike-neukirchen', '', '', '2022-05-26 03:43:53', '2022-05-26 03:43:53', '', 0, 'http://admedicum.test/?post_type=empleados&#038;p=353', 0, 'empleados', '', 0),
(354, 1, '2022-05-25 06:23:01', '2022-05-25 06:23:01', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vera holds a PhD in Health Sciences. She has in depth knowledge and practical experience in patient engagement in medical decision making, especially through patient preference analysis.&nbsp; She is experienced in interviewing patients, conducting patient surveys, and collaborating with various actors in the health care sector. She joined admedicum in May 2022.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Co</strong>ntact:&nbsp;vera.vennedey@admedicum.com</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Experience:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>More than 8 years of professional experience in the health care sector</li><li>Experience in working with patients and their relatives and friends, patient organizations, physicians and nurses in clinical practice and research</li><li>Previous collaborations with HTA organizations, health insurances, pharmaceutical companies, and medtech companies</li><li>Familiar with planning, coordinating and/or analyzing qualitative and quantitative studies including e.g., clinical trials, cross-sectional studies patient surveys, and patient preference analyses&nbsp;</li><li>Detailed methodological knowledge and practical experience in completing HTA processes within the German health care system</li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Education:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vera completed her bachelor’s degree in European Public Health (B.Sc., 2012) and her master`s degree in Health Services Research (M.Sc., 2014) at the University Maastricht. Both her master’s thesis and her PhD at the University of Cologne, addressed various aspects of involving patients in medical decision making. She investigated individual and population-related health decisions with a focus on patient preference analysis.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\